 delivers up to 15 hours of bright light on a single charge, ideal for blackout preparedness, to include with camping gear, survival kits and much more</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">RECHARGEABLE BATTERY: 750 mAh capacity fully recharges in just 4 hours and powers up to 15 hours of flashlight use or 14 hours of AM/FM radio operation</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">MULTIPLE CHARGING OPTIONS: Stay powered anywhere with USB-C charging (cable included) or hand-crank generator; 1 minute of cranking provides 5 minutes of light, 5 minutes of radio, or 1 minute of emergency alarm</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">EMERGENCY POWER BANK: Doubles as a portable charger with USB-A output to keep smartphones and small devices powered when outlets aren’t available</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">AM/FM RADIO: Tuning and volume controls with AM (520–1710 MHz) and FM (87.5–108 MHz) reception keep you informed during storms, disasters, or off-grid adventures; easy to use tuning and volume dials</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>ASR Outdoor 4 in 1 Hand Crank Emergency AM/FM Weather Radio with Flashlight, Power Bank, Alarm Siren for Camping Gear Survival Kits</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">34.99</span></h2>\n                <p>Be ready for any situation with this 4 in 1 Emergency Hand Crank Radio, Flashlight, Power Bank and Siren from ASR Outdoor, your all-in-one survival tool for light, power and communication. Whether you’re preparing for a power outage, camping off grid, or building an emergency kit, this compact device ensures you stay safe, connected and informed.<br><br>Equipped with a bright LED flashlight and a built-in 750mAh rechargeable battery, it delivers up to 15 hours of reliable light or 14 hours of AM/FM radio play on a single charge. Multiple charging options—including USB-C fast charging and a hand-crank generator—make it easy to stay powered anywhere. Just one minute of cranking gives you 5 minutes of light, 5 minutes of radio, or 1 minute of emergency siren use.<br><br>This versatile device also works as a portable power bank, featuring a USB-A output to charge smartphones and small electronics when outlets aren’t available. The AM/FM radio provides clear reception for news or weather updates, keeping you informed during storms, disasters or outdoor adventures.<br><br>Compact and lightweight at just 5\" x 2-1/4\", the two-tone gray and black design easily fits into emergency kits, bug-out bags, backpacks or glove compartments. With its built in emergency siren, intuitive controls, and durable construction, this survival radio flashlight is a must have emergency preparedness item.<br><br>Stay prepared, stay safe, and stay connected with the ASR Outdoor 4 in 1 Emergency Multitool, a must-have for every outdoor enthusiast.</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n        